title: DarcoD
author: DarcoD
content: Hi folks, I created a simple application that checks warranty expiration dates on multiple Antminer, Whatsminer, Canaan, and Alpha Miner serial numbers. Provide a list of SN's in excel format, and the program will create a new excel file showing the warranty expiration data for each serial number.You can check it out by going here: https://www.cryptominerwarranty.com/Cheers!Darco
